description: Spelling Quest is a super fun, level based spelling game for Alexa. Challenge your spelling skills with 100s of levels of gameplay. Improve and learn as the difficulty increases as you move along. Get a new word each time you retry a level. You'll never be bored again! Don't wait, 'Start Spelling Quest' now!
name: Spelling Quest
shortDescription: Super fun level based Spelling game for Alexa! 100s of levels with increasing difficulty!
